                The Prime Minister (Mr. Churchill)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-20457d5c-22fb-4ce1-a217-51d96c7c3e4b" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
