<p class="">I do not remember using the word "guarantees."</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-ec007221-50e8-4245-961e-a3186d402ecf" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
